data.description: Storage galore in this spacious 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom Colonial with 4 season sunroom would make a perfect home office. Formal dining room with window seat, 1st floor bathroom, galley style kitchen with stackable washer and dryer, living room with beautiful built-in bookshelves complete the first floor. 2nd floor features a full bath with walk-in shower, newer double hung windows, 2 nice size bedrooms and a dressing room. 1 Car detached garage with shed. Covered front porch for relaxing after a long day. 3 Parcels with this home.
